-- MOVES-Newedge strengthens capital introduction, advisory teams 
-- 
-- Tue Nov 18, 2014 05:21PM EST
-- None



Nov 18 (Reuters) - Newedge, a derivatives broker owned by Societe Generale <SOGN.PA>, made three appointments in its capital introduction and advisory teams as part of efforts to boost services in North America.

The company named Daniel Rizzuto head of capital introductions Americas. Rizzuto, who has over 25 years of experience in the alternative investment industry, will be based in New York.